title: Was Beto O’Rourke Arrested Twice and Part of a Band Called El Paso Pussycats?
subtitle: We do know he was in a punk band in the 1990s that got its name from the Icelandic word for "Waterfall."
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: Beto O'Rourke was in a band called the El Paso Pussycats and was arrested at least twice in the 1990s.
